{"tid":1130570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"祖國之拳，強國無影腳，他媽的往死裡打","createTime":"2019-04-29T06:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T07:05:52.000Z","uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c07ab63f2a847fe9d15de210d327d73e14c96d7f","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"去片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lWqYNIU1-_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlWqYNIU1-_w&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=3b77fd53\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lWqYNIU1-_w</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜我手殘，錄唔切片頭<br />\n<br />\n事緣今日要出差上深圳，旅遊巴停係某站時候<br />\n幾個強國人上車。<br />\n大肚婆&amp;老公上先，企係車頭坐位隔離，除袋，但後面個北方地中海阿叔急住坐低，疑似撞開大肚婆，坐去後面。<br />\n因為太突然，我開唔切電話錄，所以係度描述俾各位聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大肚婆老公光頭佬就出聲鬧，吊鳩阿叔撞到大肚婆，阿叔亦不甘示弱，搬光頭佬祖先出黎。<br />\n叫囂對峙冇十秒，懷疑地中海阿叔望清大肚婆老公個樣後，預視到自己將來都係光頭，不安感大增，終於忍唔住使出祖國排雲掌，開始推撞，但佢老味，隔住個阿姐推落個大肚婆身，光頭佬忍唔住，一拳超人上身，隔住兩個身位一個小箭步左衝拳打落地中海阿叔頭頂，吊佢老母，哩幕冇錄到！分享唔到個股熱血俾各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就係片入面各位見到嘅，地中海大叔使出無影腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人叫報警，而我錄都係因為想做證據俾阿sir，可惜最後報警阿姐俾人叫停，而事件都告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n好彩個小妹妹同大肚婆都冇"},{"pid":"81994f5e870a5f9d4dce2c6d4752c060f1655d28","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"當時我都好撚熱血，好想夾擊個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但趕住上去整野忍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bd223b6246372b9cfbea257c76243290706931","tid":1130570,"uid":70159,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"屌 乜撚都睇唔到點做戰地記者架你"},{"pid":"f6964481255f4e34cab240f825b52a2449d77d22","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3bd223b6246372b9cfbea257c76243290706931","tid":1130570,"uid":70159,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"屌 乜撚都睇唔到點做戰地記者架你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住拋磚，睇下同車有冇連登巴絲錄到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73285b02fda7107b616448d438359893002405d4","tid":1130570,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81994f5e870a5f9d4dce2c6d4752c060f1655d28","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"當時我都好撚熱血，好想夾擊個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但趕住上去整野忍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"完全感受到你個種熱血"},{"pid":"5506a48c4fabf4c4e9ced900ecc328ff929cc23d","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73285b02fda7107b616448d438359893002405d4","tid":1130570,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81994f5e870a5f9d4dce2c6d4752c060f1655d28","tid":1130570,"uid":141419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"當時我都好撚熱血，好想夾擊個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但趕住上去整野忍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"完全感受到你個種熱血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"第一團熱血係見到蝗鬥<br />\n第二團係因為大肚婆都恰<br />\n強國人死性不改，係鍾意狗咬狗"}]}